Subject: Re: Performance when computing computing a filter using hundreds of diff terms.
Date: Fri, 6 Aug 2004 22:59:52 +0200
User-Agent: KMail/1.5.4
References: <4112A758.6010700@newsmonster.org>
In-Reply-To: <4112A758.6010700@newsmonster.org>
MIME-Version: 1.0
